// Level 1: Single Pattern Learning Test
// Success Criteria: 80%+ correct execution
//
// Task: Learn that context A leads to goal G via operation ^left
// Then when A is observed and G is desired, execute ^left

*volume=100
*setopname 1 ^left

// === LEARNING PHASE ===
// Teach: A → ^left → G

<context --> A>. :|:
10
^left. :|:
10
<goal --> achieved>. :|:
100

// === TESTING PHASE ===
// Present context A and desire goal G
// System should execute ^left

<context --> A>. :|:
1
<goal --> achieved>! :|:
1
